#. <a class="sc" id="sc29"></a>
msgctxt "mn41:15.1"
msgid "Ākaṅkheyya ce, gahapatayo, dhammacārī samacārī:"
msgstr "A person of principled and moral conduct might wish:"

msgctxt "mn41:15.2"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā khattiyamahāsālānaṃ sahabyataṃ "
"upapajjeyyan’ti;"
msgstr ""
"‘If only, when my body breaks up, after death, I would be reborn in the "
"company of well-to-do aristocrats!’"

msgctxt "mn41:15.3"
msgid ""
"ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ vijjati, yaṃ so kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā "
"khattiyamahāsālānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjeyya."
msgstr "It’s possible that this might happen."

msgctxt "mn41:15.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "mn41:15.5"
msgid "Tathā hi so dhammacārī samacārī."
msgstr "Because they have principled and moral conduct."

