#. <a class="nya" id="nya43"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc35"></a>
msgctxt "mn41:43.1"
msgid "Ākaṅkheyya ce, gahapatayo, dhammacārī samacārī:"
msgstr "A person of principled and moral conduct might wish:"

msgctxt "mn41:43.2"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva "
"dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyyan’ti;"
msgstr ""
"‘If only I might realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by "
"wisdom in this very life, and live having realized it with my own insight "
"due to the ending of defilements.’"

msgctxt "mn41:43.3"
msgid ""
"ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ vijjati, yaṃ so āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ "
"paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja "
"vihareyya."
msgstr "It’s possible that this might happen."

msgctxt "mn41:43.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "mn41:43.5"
msgid "Tathā hi so dhammacārī samacārī”ti."
msgstr "Because they have principled and moral conduct.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya44"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.290"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc36"></a>
msgctxt "mn41:44.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, sāleyyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"When he had spoken, the brahmins and householders of Sālā said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "mn41:44.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama."
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent!"

msgctxt "mn41:44.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā "
"vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya:"
" ‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evamevaṃ bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena "
"dhammo pakāsito."
msgstr ""
"As if he were righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing "
"out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark so people with good "
"eyes can see what’s there, Master Gotama has made the teaching clear in many "
"ways."

msgctxt "mn41:44.4"
msgid ""
"Ete mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāma dhammañca bhikkhusaṃghañca."
msgstr ""
"We go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the teaching, and to the mendicant "
"Saṅgha."

#. VAR: pāṇupete → pāṇupetaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "mn41:44.5"
msgid "Upāsake no bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupete saraṇaṃ gate”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember us as lay followers who have "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
